OL,3,CIs the streaming revolution putting UK
OL,4,CTV dramas at risk?
OL,6,FThe streaming services have brought a
OL,7,Fviewing revolution to our screens: big
OL,8,FUS companies with deep pockets
OL,9,Foffering a wealth of choice to viewers.
OL,11,FBut some leading industry figures here
OL,12,Fsay the streamers' focus on making
OL,13,Fcontent that has a global reach is
OL,14,Fputting homegrown UK-focused stories
OL,15,Fin high-end drama at risk.
OL,17,FMaking series like the huge hit Mr
OL,18,FBates v The Post Office is reported to
OL,19,Fhave left ITV with a loss of #1
OL,20,Fmillion last year, even though it was
OL,21,Fthe most watched programme of 2024.
