OL,6,FThe need for domestic broadcasters to
OL,7,Fmake drama that can be sold abroad to
OL,8,Frecoup costs has raised fears that
OL,9,FBritish stories may be getting
OL,10,Fsqueezed out in the future.
OL,12,FPeter Kosminsky the award-winning
OL,13,Fdirector of Wolf Hall and its sequel
OL,14,FThe Mirror and the Light said he would
OL,15,Fnever be able to afford to make a
OL,16,Fdrama like this in the current climate.
