OL,3,CIs the streaming revolution putting UK
OL,4,CTV dramas at risk?
OL,6,FCompetition from streamers, freezes in
OL,7,Fthe BBC licence fee, a drop in
OL,8,Fadvertising revenue not to mention
OL,9,Finflation and the ongoing impact of
OL,10,Fthe recent industry strikes in the US,
OL,11,Fhave made the environment in the
OL,12,Findustry more difficult to navigate.
OL,14,FHis proposal backed by a parliamentary
OL,15,Fcommittee of a 5% levy on revenue from
OL,16,Fstreaming services' UK subscriptions
OL,17,Fcould, he says, be used to help the
OL,18,Findustry here.
