OL,6,FThere are widespread calls for
OL,7,Fenhanced tax incentives, particularly
OL,8,Ffrom those mainly freelance people,
OL,9,Fworking in the Unscripted sector,
OL,10,Fthings like documentaries, travel
OL,11,Fshows and reality TV.
OL,13,FRecent figures from the union Bectu
OL,14,Fseen by ITV News, show a slight
OL,15,Fimprovement in some areas from a few
OL,16,Fmonths ago but still some alarming
OL,17,Ffigures, including 43% of those
OL,18,Fsurveyed saying they're currently out
OL,19,Fof work and a third seeing themselves
OL,20,Fleaving the industry in the next five
OL,21,Fyears.
